description:
Manufactured by America`s Armalite company, Ichihachi is http://anidb.net/ch39931 [Ichiroku]`s cousin. She`s a member of the class next to http://anidb.net/ch39929 [Funko] and the others as well as Funko`s roommate in the dorms. She`s probably the one with the most common sense.
Source: ANN
name: Ichihachi
